"Boulevard hits a home run with this vastly simple yet delicious barrel aged sour ale. The nose is sour and somewhat acidic with a vinegar like aroma but it keeps a natural cherry tone. The flavor is simple as well but mixes the vanilla of the barrel and tart cherry to create a great tasting ale. There are tones of cocoa butter, with creaminess, and a move towards a Flemish Sour as you continue to drink. Not too tart or sour this is easy and flavorful."
